
	Usage

  $ make
  $ ./polyfit '0,1' '1,0'
  P(x) =  - 1.000000 x + 1.000000
  $ ./polyfit '-1,0' '0,0' '1,0'
  P(x) = 0.500000 x^2 + 0.500000 x


